metadata.name: 6 things
metadata.description:
6 key things in the last 6 years has transformed me a lot and has allowed me to climb up the ladder to where I am now. If these 6 things didn’t happen to me I wouldn’t have achieved what I have achieved.

The 6 things were: my parents getting divorced, me tearing my ACL, catching the flu, getting infections, catching covid-19, and loosing my dad to gun violence.

In this artwork you can see those 6 things, me rising above all 6 things, and the key lesson learned from those 6 things.
